title: Walking path to Panagia Kalamiotisa (Anafi, Greece)
name: Walking path to Panagia Kalamiotisa (Anafi, Greece)
description: Kalamos, is the 2nd largest rock of the Mediterranean sea and is part of the Greek island Anafi. The chapel of "Panagia Kalamiotisa" is built on top of Kalamos. This is the path you have to walk to get to the chapel and enjoy the great view of the Aegean sea -and the feeling of real freedom!
